{
	"info": {
		"name": "Eurobase Edge Functions",
		"description": "Tests for Edge Functions CRUD, invocation, triggers, versioning, and metrics.\n\n## Setup\n\n1. Gateway running\n2. Migrations 026-028 applied\n3. `platform_token`, `project_id`, `anon_key`, and `end_user_token` set",
